{"tid":1068822,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"騎住逆線俾岀停車場既車撞到車頭","createTime":"2019-03-19T13:29:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T10:08:05.000Z","uid":18310,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9420926c631750837bfa5c6a2c112aa3709d4054","tid":1068822,"uid":18310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:29:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZMsnbCv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZMsnbCv.png&h=2efac1b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當係呢條路(真實地方唔方便講,條路窄好多，車場亦係有蓋停車場)<br />\n左邊有一架死車同一架行駛ing既單車，咁我就騎住右邊逆線過死車同單車。<br />\n到過左單車準備收線即時候，停車場就有架車駛岀黎撞到我車頭右邊車頭燈後邊。<br />\n<br />\n我想問有冇機會兩個都告不小心駕駛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac0444e77caed13a2d7b0e79ffcdbee596004b7","tid":1068822,"uid":141424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:32:18.000Z","msg":"考牌就比騎 沙駕河畔線<br />\n停車場出就應該係一路出大路<br />\n正路就出停車場避大路"},{"pid":"4fcb5d32f02319fbfcadadfb789bdb360ab571b0","tid":1068822,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:32:19.000Z","msg":"咁複雜<br />\n留名睇答案"},{"pid":"d387da8a3860eef9412077eb2c4c4b9e94a2e030","tid":1068822,"uid":18310,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zv89A8c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZv89A8c.png&h=3cf992f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n類似咁撞，但我係黑色車，同埋撞既係右邊"},{"pid":"aefd8fdcf6bbf1e249d8b8b2126fef443ddc8b11","tid":1068822,"uid":18310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ac0444e77caed13a2d7b0e79ffcdbee596004b7","tid":1068822,"uid":141424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:32:18.000Z","msg":"考牌就比騎 沙駕河畔線<br />\n停車場出就應該係一路出大路<br />\n正路就出停車場避大路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:37:49.000Z","msg":"我問過幾個都係小路岀大路責任大，但自問都非正線(有單車L)所以想睇下會唔會告埋我"},{"pid":"42278be8f8d20618e5e12ace4afe11c079f49e38","tid":1068822,"ui